#EXDESC
ExDescKey    chalkboard chalk board~
ExDesc       Welcome to Channels/Talking Class. In order to effectively communicate on
this mud one needs to know the proper "channels" to use. In order to use a
channel one must have a "comlink" in their inventory or on their person.
To use a certain channel one must type the proper extension then what they
wish to say. For more help on channels you can type help channels.
 
~
#ENDEXDESC

#EXDESC
ExDescKey    chalkboard chalk board~
ExDesc       Welcome to the Communications class. ere you will learn how to communicate
with the rest of the mud. A necessary piece of equipment, the CDI, is
provided for you. This device helps you communicate to others. In order to
use any of the channels such as tell, ooc, ic(role play), shout or yell
one must have a CDI in their inventory or equipped. As a newbie you have
very few channels avaible to you. Newbie, Tells and Replies are readily
avaible for your use. For more help on channels type help channel.
 
~
#ENDEXDESC

#ENDROOM

