#EXDESC
ExDescKey    chalkboard chalk board~
ExDesc       Welcome to Moving Class. We all Have to get around somehow in this mud and
we do that with directions. ALthough some muds have North, South, East,
West, Up ,Down, Northeast, Southeast, Northwest, Southwest, We only have
the normal directions. North, South, East, West, Up and Down. To move in
any of these directions you must either type the first letter for example
d to go down or the entire word. Moving about is easy so long as you know
where you can move to. By typing look you can see which directions the
exits of a room lead.
 
~
#ENDEXDESC

