#EXDESC
ExDescKey    chalk board chalkboard~
ExDesc       Flying is rather quite easy once you get used to it. But first you will
have to buy a suit. Once you have picked out a suit, Type "Allships",
it'll bring up a list of suits/ships you  can purchase. The ones with
prices beside them are buyable, the other ones with names belong to other
people. Once you have found the suit you want to buy, type "buyship <name
of  suit/ship>". But before you try and fly, go learn the skills "Mobile
Suits", "Navigation", "Ship Systems", and "Weapon Systems". After that, go
to your suit, and type "open <suit  name>", then "enter <suit name>". Once
inside, type "Launch", you may fail on your first few tries, but keep on
typing launch till you take off.
~
