#EXDESC
ExDescKey    chalkboard chalk board~
ExDesc       Welcome to Engineering Basics 101. In order to advance in Engineering you
must learn a few things first. The first skill you learn in Engineering is
makecontainer. Now to do this one must have the proper tools. Cloth and a
sewing kit are necessary. In order to make a container one must have the
sewing kit and cloth in their inventory. To make a container you must also
specify the containers location and the name of the container. For example
to make a container worn on the body named Light type "makecontainer body
Light". You can get creative with where and the name of your containers.
For more help type help makecontainer.
 
~
